openadk.library.impl
Interface ISIFPrimitives

All Known Implementing Classes:
SIFPrimitives
public interface ISIFPrimitives

The ISIFPrimitives interface is implemented by internal ADK classes that implement primitive SIF messaging functionality such as SIF_Register, SIF_Event, and SIF_SystemControl. Internal ADK classes always delegate low-level SIF functions to the global ISIFPrimitives object provided by the static ADK.getPrimitives method.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Eric Petersen
